        <Parent_String>Eastern Zhou [300018374], Zhou (culture) [300018372], Chinese dynastic styles and periods [300018353], Chinese (culture or style) [300018322], East Asian [300018321], Asian [300018279], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
